OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783702080
OL,3,CTwo taken to hospital after fire in
OL,4,CWood Green
OL,6,FTwo people have been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital, after eighty firefighters
OL,8,Fwere called to put out a building fire
OL,9,Fin Wood Green.
OL,11,FBoth individuals were taken away by
OL,12,Fthe London Ambulance Service to be
OL,13,Ftreated for smoke inhalation.
OL,15,FThe fire brigade first received calls
OL,16,Fabout the fire at 21:25 last night,
OL,17,Fwhich affected two adjoining buildings
OL,18,Fon High Road.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
