PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1783702080
OL,3,CTwo taken to hospital after fire in
OL,4,CWood Green
OL,6,FNine people were led to safety by
OL,7,Fcrews wearing breathing apparatus,
OL,8,Fwhile six others were rescued from a
OL,9,Fflat roof by firefighters via a short
OL,10,Fextension ladder.
OL,12,FThe fire was brought under control
OL,13,Fjust after midnight, but firefighters
OL,14,Fhave remained on the site overnight to
OL,15,Ffully extinguish the fire.
OL,17,FRoad closures on High Road near the
OL,18,Fjunction with Turnpike Lane were put
OL,19,Fin place, but have now ended.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
